{"tid":617561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瘋傳「人妻偷情外遇」性愛片　要女友身敗名裂","createTime":"2018-04-05T05:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T15:40:36.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4c4aecf7f07964dc7f8fe23c93924dbe93d3eb5b","tid":617561,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:14:42.000Z","msg":"不滿她還有其他情人，竊錄2人性愛影片上傳至《YouTube》及其前夫等人，要她身敗名裂，自己也成階下囚。<br />\n今日出版的《自由時報》報導，林姓男子與陳姓女子原為男女朋友，但不滿自己不是唯一，去年7月以微型攝影機竊錄兩人愛撫及性行為過程，先給陳女前夫觀看，又上傳至《YouTube》網站，標題寫著「人妻偷情外遇」，傳送給認識陳女的多名友人及供不特定多數人上網點閱觀覽。<br />\n林男目的要她身敗名裂，陳女到庭表示不願意原諒林男，新竹地院依散布竊錄非公開活動罪與恐嚇危害安全罪，將林男判刑6月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180405/1328816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180405%2F1328816&d=OBFoKsiX%2BH3Sc29xeXp75r%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=cd145b54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180405%2F1328816&h=930c8fff\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180405/1328816</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4378d8248a31298bc597996821e0e2d5be90be46","tid":617561,"uid":72054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:17:29.000Z","msg":"瘋傳"},{"pid":"ae3b7f40036b03dbcfdb933a1cb9aecd0eb203bd","tid":617561,"uid":985,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:21:42.000Z","msg":"網絡孤島"},{"pid":"1d8854ac42cdc857dd8b4f61c0358ad137d09623","tid":617561,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae3b7f40036b03dbcfdb933a1cb9aecd0eb203bd","tid":617561,"uid":985,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:21:42.000Z","msg":"網絡孤島"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:22:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk